I. COLLECTION OF INFORMATION
We collect certain Personal Data when you use our Services. Personal Data is typically data that identifies an individual or relates to an identifiable individual, though the definition of Personal Data depends on the applicable law where you are located. Only the definition that applies to your physical location will apply to you under this Policy. The Personal Data that we collect depends on your interactions with us, and the choices you make.
The Personal Data that we collect from you, either directly or indirectly, will depend on how you interact with us and the Platform. Such Personal Data broadly falls into the following categories:
Information That You Voluntarily Provide to Us:
The types of Personal Data that we or third-party service providers who assist us (in providing, maintaining, and operating our business and Services) collect from you include:
Account Registration.
We may collect information relating to the creation of an account, such as your email address and phone number. We also collect account information from third parties such as Apple, Google, and Facebook, based on your authorization. We combine such account information with your POIZON account so that you may login and access our Services directly through your third-party account.
Account Personalization.
We may collect your profile picture, nickname, gender, and date of birth. Your nickname and profile picture will be publicly displayed, should you provide them.
Seller Account Registration
. We may collect your first and last name, phone number, email address, region/country.
Seller Order Placement
. We may collect your information when you sell your goods through our Services, including, for example, your first and last name, address, postal code, email address, phone number, geo-location, and third-party payment information.
Buyer Order Placement.
We are PCI-DSS certified, and we comply with the Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard when processing your payment card information. We may collect your Personal Data when you place an order through our Services, including, for example, your first and last name, delivery address, postal code, email address, phone number, and payment account or credit card information.
Customer Support.
When you engage with our support team and customer support providers, we may collect records, copies of your correspondence (including email addresses), or additional information you choose to share with us.
Promotions and Feedback
. We may collect information relating to your voluntary participation in a promotion or survey that we may ask you to complete for research purposes.
Newsletter Sign-ups.
You may choose to provide us your email address if you wish to receive promotional emails from us with news and exclusive offers.
Device Permissions and Third-Party Services.
We may collect information relating to your use of features of our Services that may ask you to grant us access to location information, photos, microphone, video camera, or media on your computer or mobile device.
Social Media.
When you interact with our Services or accounts on a social media platform, we may collect the information that you or the platform make available to us on that page or account, including your social media account ID and/or user name associated with that social media service, your profile picture, email address, friends list or information about the people and groups you are connected to and how you interact with them, and any information you have made public in connection with that social media service. When you follow our POIZON social media accounts, we may interact with you through comments and/or direct messages. When you follow our Discord group, we may also regularly post advertisements in the group.
