Purchase Information.
Details of the products you purchased or services you used, such as the product images you provided when using the Platform's authentication service.
Payment Information.
Credit card or similar payment information that you intend to purchase with; billing and delivery address. Payment information is collected through a third- party payment gateway and we do not store payment card information. Depending on your jurisdiction, you may also need to provide additional information related to customs and taxes, for example a VAT ID.
Social Media Information.
Where you are a certified blogger or influencer for us, information such as your contact and social media account/blog information.
Events and sweepstakes.
If you enter an event or sweepstakes sponsored by us, you may provide us with your name, date of birth, mailing address and e-mail address. If you enter through a social media platform, you will provide your social media handle and potentially other Personal Data as part of your entry.
Surveys and reviews.
If you have chosen to receive marketing messages from us, we may contact you to participate in surveys about the Services or provide product or service reviews. If you decide to participate, you may be asked to provide Personal Data.
Identity Verification Information.
Under certain circumstances and in accordance with various regulations, we may need to further verify your identity. To do this, we may request that you provide government photo identification, additional data such as Tax identification number, Bank account and/or a live photo to our identity verification provider, which can confirm the data provided. It is also the case that when you register with a phone number and/or email, a verification code will be sent to you to validate your account registration information.
